@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get paged projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Search projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?search=dotnet&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Filter projects by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?status=Completed&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Search and filter projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects?search=api&status=Planning&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5

### Create project
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Portfolio Tracker API",
  "description": "A professional .NET API for tracking developer portfolio projects.",
  "repositoryUrl": "https://github.com/birabotto/portfolio-tracker-api",
  "demoUrl": null,
  "techStack": ".NET, EF Core, PostgreSQL, Docker, GitHub Actions"
}

### Get project by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Update project
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Portfolio Tracker API",
  "description": "Updated project description.",
  "repositoryUrl": "https://github.com/birabotto/portfolio-tracker-api",
  "demoUrl": "https://example.com",
  "techStack": ".NET, EF Core, PostgreSQL, Docker, GitHub Actions",
  "status": "Completed"
}

### Delete project
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
